{"tid":1898863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警葵涌邨拘15人稱「老師帶學生犯法」　消息：被捕教師與該批學生無直接關係","createTime":"2020-02-26T09:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T10:39:23.000Z","uid":6497,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff75b0dcfeffbcb170956647f4430650133abf3","tid":1898863,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs2.mingpao.com/ins/20200226/S00001/054715109a1629042e49b085531ef2bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs2.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200226%2FS00001%2F054715109a1629042e49b085531ef2bb.png&h=cb82e09b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://fs2.mingpao.com/ins/20200226/S00001/054d4d02d94c5648d9b514e091c1845d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs2.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200226%2FS00001%2F054d4d02d94c5648d9b514e091c1845d.jpg&h=53874c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方昨日（25日）透過facebook短片稱，關注葵涌邨一宗刑毁案中「有老師帶住學生去犯案」，絕不是文明社會接受，呼籲家長及學校多關注年輕人。本報接獲消息稱，被捕的15人中僅一人為教師，任教馬鞍山一間中學，其餘14名被捕者中無一為該校學生，暫未有證據證明他們互相認識。<br />\n<br />\n警方前日（24日）於葵涌邨一平台拘捕8男7女，年齡介乎14至29歲，涉嫌在該處聚集和在牆身張貼海報，並檢獲多張海報和一批膠水，15人涉嫌刑事毁壞被捕。<br />\n<br />\n葵青區議員梁錦威表示，被捕的8男7女中，7名女子已先後獲保釋，而其餘8名男子則選擇拒絕保釋，預計最快於今晚（25日）得知會否被起訴。"},{"pid":"74708e991bf73a51af6659ed2362fdaeed3496d2","tid":1898863,"uid":175346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cdaaa5e09591faae459c593819be2a5232f67f7","tid":1898863,"uid":11628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"又預備搞到人無左份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ea1b09c5ed45842403f2a0a271e00088335237","tid":1898863,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200226/s00001/1582704381599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F